<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Dein Anmeldecode</title>
  <style type="text/css">
      * {
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
          font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
          font-size: 16px;
          line-height: 1.6;
          color: #2d3748;
          background-color: #E1ECF4;
          -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
          width: 100%;
          padding: 32px 16px;
          background-color: #E1ECF4;
      }

      .email-container {
          max-width: 600px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          background: #ffffff;
          border-radius: 8px;
          overflow: hidden;
          border: 1px solid #cacaca;
      }

      /* Header */
      .email-header {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28538F 0%, #2c5282 100%);
          padding: 32px 40px;
          text-align: left;
      }

      .email-header__logo {
          display: inline-block;
          width: 36px;
          height: 36px;
          background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
          border-radius: 6px;
          text-align: center;
          line-height: 36px;
          color: #fff;
          font-weight: 700;
          font-size: 16px;
          margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .email-header h1 {
          color: #ffffff;
          font-size: 22px;
          font-weight: 700;
          margin: 0 0 4px;
      }

      .email-header p {
          color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
          font-size: 14px;
          margin: 0;
      }

      /* Badge */
      .email-badge {
          display: inline-block;
          background: #fef7eb;
          color: #d4922a;
          font-size: 12px;
          font-weight: 700;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.08em;
          padding: 4px 12px;
          border-radius: 100px;
          margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      /* Body */
      .email-body {
          padding: 32px 40px;
      }

      .email-body h2 {
          font-size: 20px;
          font-weight: 700;
          color: #2c5282;
          margin: 0 0 8px;
      }

      .email-body p {
          font-size: 15px;
          line-height: 1.7;
          color: #2d3748;
          margin: 0 0 12px;
      }

      /* Divider */
      .email-divider {
          border: none;
          height: 2px;
          background: #e8a838;
          margin: 24px 0;
          width: 60px;
      }

      /* Code Box */
      .email-code-box {
          background: #E1ECF4;
          border: 2px solid #28538F;
          border-radius: 8px;
          padding: 32px 20px;
          margin: 24px 0;
          text-align: center;
      }

      .email-code-box__label {
          font-size: 13px;
          font-weight: 600;
          color: #718096;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.08em;
          margin: 0 0 16px;
      }

      .email-code-box__code {
          font-size: 38px;
          font-weight: 700;
          color: #28538F;
          letter-spacing: 0.5em;
          font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
          margin: 0 0 16px;
          display: block;
      }

      .email-code-box__hint {
          font-size: 13px;
          color: #718096;
          margin: 0;
      }

      /* Warning */
      .email-warning {
          background: #fffbeb;
          border-left: 4px solid #e8a838;
          border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
          padding: 14px 18px;
          margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .email-warning p {
          font-size: 13px;
          color: #92400e;
          margin: 0;
      }

      /* Signature */
      .email-signature {
          margin-top: 24px;
          padding-top: 16px;
          border-top: 1px solid #dedee4;
      }

      .email-signature p {
          font-size: 14px;
          color: #718096;
          margin: 0;
      }

      .email-signature strong {
          color: #2d3748;
      }

      /* Footer */
      .email-footer {
          background: #2c5282;
          padding: 20px 40px;
          text-align: center;
      }

      .email-footer p {
          color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
          font-size: 12px;
          margin: 0 0 4px;
      }

      .email-footer a {
          color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
          text-decoration: none;
      }

      /* Responsive */
      @media only screen and (max-width: 640px) {
          .email-body,
          .email-header,
          .email-footer {
              padding-left: 20px !important;
              padding-right: 20px !important;
          }

          .email-header h1 {
              font-size: 18px !important;
          }

          .email-code-box__code {
              font-size: 48px !important;
              letter-spacing: 0.4em !important;
          }
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-wrapper">
  <div class="email-container">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="email-header">
      <div class="email-header__logo">B</div>
      <h1>buero-dienstleistungen.com</h1>
      <p>Ihr Portal für Bürodienstleistungen</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="email-body">
      <span class="email-badge">✦ Anmeldung</span>

      <h2>Dein Anmeldecode</h2>
      <hr class="email-divider">

      <p>Hallo <%= @user.email %>,</p>
      <p>du hast eine Anmeldung angefordert. Gib den folgenden Code ein, um dich einzuloggen:</p>

      <!-- Code Box -->
      <div class="email-code-box">
        <p class="email-code-box__label">Dein Einmalcode</p>
        <h4 class="email-code-box__code" style="font-size:38px;font-weight:700;color:#28538F;letter-spacing:0.5em;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;margin:0 0 16px;display:block;"><%= @auth_code %></h4>
        <p class="email-code-box__hint">⏱ Gültig für 5 Minuten</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Sicherheitshinweis -->
      <div class="email-warning">
        <p>⚠️ Du hast diese Anmeldung nicht angefordert? Dann ignoriere diese E-Mail einfach – dein Konto bleibt sicher.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Signatur -->
      <div class="email-signature">
        <p>Herzliche Grüße</p>
        <p><strong>Werner Laude</strong></p>
        <p>buero-dienstleistungen.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>© <%= Date.current.year %> buero-dienstleistungen.com · Alle Rechte vorbehalten</p>
      <p><a href="https://www.buero-dienstleistungen.com">www.buero-dienstleistungen.com</a></p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
